  "doc_id": "46219",
  "text": "The forms are constructed in analogy to previous preclinical CDEs by the National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke (NINDS) for traumatic brain injury research. [CITATION_1] CDEs generated by the EPITARGET consortium (Targets and Biomarkers for Antiepileptogenesis) served as useful templates for our TASK3 Physiology working group. [CITATION_2] The proposed recommendations originate mostly from previously published methods used for rodent physiology research.",
